content:
I am noticing fake FB profiles for Tim Walz. And my FB group has a member that appears to be Doug Emhoff with 500 followers and no checkmark. Is the Harris team staying on top of this? They are posting positive things, but I am concerned that they will suddenly post crazy stuff in October and gullible voters will think it is real. Is this one real? If so, why no checkmark?

https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61565131434103&mibextid=LQQJ4d

Hi there! Thank you for raising this concern. We don't handle this on our server team since we're the online (from home) volunteer branch of the campaign, but staff who sees this can pass it along to the right place for assessment. Thank you!
